A toy raytracer.
Joe Doliner

compiling:
This project is known to work on 64bit Ubuntu with libxml installed. It should work fine on 32 bit

build:
cd build
make

documentation:
cd build
make doc

running:
examples scenes can be found in /examples

to run them:
cd build
./tracer ../examples/name.xml

output will be written as output.ppm
